The quotient space $\F_2^E/\row(B_G)$ is canonically dual to $\Ker(B_G)=\mathcal{C}(G)$, and the
restriction of the rows of $\Lambda_\Gamma$ to $\mathcal{C}(G)$ is precisely the cycle-label map.
